289
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:41,700
Don't worry. I've arranged everything.

290
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:43,680
This is a professional driver.

291
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,160
Poor bodyguard.

292
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:47,680
You aren't observant at all.

293
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:51,520
Here.

294
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,460
Not this one?

295
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:04,581
Hello, ladies.

296
00:19:04,581 --> 00:19:06,861
Which one of you is Miss Yan?

297
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:09,620
So, this is your fancy cart?

298
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:12,140
That's right. Fancy cart.

299
00:19:12,140 --> 00:19:14,280
Yeah. Let's get in.

300
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:17,440
Come on. Hold on tight.

301
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,560
We're about to go.

302
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:24,760
I've got this too.

