304
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:52,860
How did this happen?

305
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:03,020
My home is still here.

306
00:20:11,601 --> 00:20:13,341
This is...

307
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,760
your home?

308
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:47,960
 Aren't we supposed to have a final division? 

309
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:50,520
 Why do you have to guard the lake? 

310
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:52,124
 Our village head is foresighted. 

311
00:20:52,124 --> 00:20:54,220
 He fears neighboring thieves. 

312
00:20:54,220 --> 00:20:56,880
 If they steal, we'll get fewer pearls. 

313
00:20:56,880 --> 00:21:00,360
 Each family will get a smaller share. 

314
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:05,640
 For Jiang Zhao's school life, we'll afford fewer erasers or pencils. 

315
00:21:05,640 --> 00:21:07,420
 Am I right? 

316
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:10,300
 I should go. 

317
00:21:10,300 --> 00:21:12,480
 Be very careful. 

318
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:14,600
 I'm wearing my talisman. 

319
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:16,220
 Don't worry. 

320
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:45,360
We're here alone.

321
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:50,800
If something is on your mind and bothers you, you can talk to me.

322
00:21:59,120 --> 00:22:01,046
You know.

323
00:22:01,046 --> 00:22:04,847
Villagers here live off pearls.

324
00:22:04,847 --> 00:22:07,172
Waters with clams are just like farmlands.

325
00:22:07,172 --> 00:22:09,200
They aren't all fertile.

326
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:12,049
Some have more clams while some have fewer.

327
00:22:12,049 --> 00:22:14,518
Everybody wants the best part.

328
00:22:14,518 --> 00:22:16,698
 Stop fighting. 

329
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:22,440
 In the division of water, we fought with the neighboring village. 

330
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:26,387
 - At first, they agreed to wait for the authorities' solution. 
 - Stop it! 

331
00:22:26,387 --> 00:22:28,760
 But guys from the neighboring village 

332
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:31,161
