333
00:22:31,161 --> 00:22:33,241
Things were out of control.

334
00:22:34,040 --> 00:22:36,780
 This is our territory! Go back to your own village. 

335
00:22:36,780 --> 00:22:38,840
 Go away. Get out of here. 

336
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:41,400
 Get away! Leave. 

337
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:43,260
 Send them away. 

338
00:22:43,260 --> 00:22:44,960
 Throw them off. 

339
00:22:46,744 --> 00:22:48,484
My father...

340
00:22:49,544 --> 00:22:52,004
fell into the water

341
00:22:52,961 --> 00:22:55,481
and died during this fight.

342
00:22:57,280 --> 00:23:01,620
But a pearl fisher should be a good swimmer.

343
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,840
That's right.

344
00:23:04,840 --> 00:23:06,740
Who knows?

345
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:14,240
Maybe he fell and cramped up.

346
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:16,780
Accidents happen.

347
00:23:16,780 --> 00:23:18,220
Right?

348
00:23:19,312 --> 00:23:21,912
We didn't even find his body.

349
00:23:25,700 --> 00:23:31,040
After he died, my mother became delirious.

350
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:33,900
She couldn't distinguish between illusion and reality.

351
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:40,680
 Mom, where are you going? 

352
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:41,960
 To see your father. 

353
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:44,920
