00:30:54,177 --> 00:30:55,837
No.

458
00:30:56,462 --> 00:30:59,027
People here honor the God of Water.

459
00:30:59,027 --> 00:31:02,387
But we don't believe in retribution.

460
00:31:29,180 --> 00:31:30,780
Here we are.

461
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:45,720
This is it?

