00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:48,120
My cart can't get through that path.

463
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:51,520
Ladies, you'll have to walk from here.

464
00:31:52,320 --> 00:31:54,760
Keep walking in this direction.

465
00:31:54,760 --> 00:31:57,560
Wuzhu Village is on the opposite hill.

466
00:31:57,560 --> 00:32:00,640
Climb up and you'll see an old ancestral hall. That's it.

467
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:02,840
Will we go along the way?

468
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:04,925
You can't go straight there.

469
00:32:04,925 --> 00:32:06,800
See? You must take the outer path.

470
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:08,360
In the middle is a swamp.

471
00:32:08,360 --> 00:32:09,941
You'll get stuck.

472
00:32:09,941 --> 00:32:12,641
Call me if you need a ride when you're back.

473
00:32:27,177 --> 00:32:28,518
Why are you going that way?

474
00:32:28,518 --> 00:32:30,479
Isn't that the center of the lake?

475
00:32:30,479 --> 00:32:33,560
There's a swamp. We'll get stuck.

476
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:37,700
Where are you going?

477
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:39,120
Let's just go straight.

478
00:32:39,120 --> 00:32:41,980
Don't take a detour. Isn't it exhausting?

479
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:51,020
According to my analysis, this terrain is like a divided soft-boiled egg.

480
00:32:51,671 --> 00:32:54,854
In the middle is the lake. Around the lake is the inaccessible swamp.

481
00:32:54,854 --> 00:32:57,020
But as it goes out, it gets more solid.

482
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:59,500
Horses and cars can ride on it.

483
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:02,360
Between two points, the straight line is the shortest.

484
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:04,600
We should walk near the center as far as we can.

485
00:33:04,600 --> 00:33:07,040
It saves time and energy.

486
00:33:41,250 --> 00:33:43,230
The lake bottom.

487
00:34:34,380 --> 00:34:36,060
Thirteen-Thousand.

488
00:34:45,680 --> 00:34:47,460
What's that noise?

489
00:34:55,449 --> 00:34:57,374
Don't need to see it.

490
00:34:57,374 --> 00:34:59,159
