494
00:35:10,340 --> 00:35:12,140
Let's take a look.

495
00:35:13,257 --> 00:35:17,137
Are you sure we'll walk there?

496
00:35:34,980 --> 00:35:37,907
What a terrible route you've chosen.

497
00:35:37,907 --> 00:35:39,288
Look.

498
00:35:39,288 --> 00:35:40,830
So what?

