00:35:55,220 --> 00:35:58,400
Do you feel there's something underground?

505
00:35:59,489 --> 00:36:01,209
No.

506
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:05,100
Don't be so suspicious.

507
00:37:06,030 --> 00:37:07,750
Thirteen-Thousand.

508
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:18,620
The food was freshly made.

509
00:37:24,280 --> 00:37:27,480
Is it the guy we saw just now?

