00:37:49,680 --> 00:37:52,920
Hey, Luo Ren. Are you in Wuzhu Village?

514
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,980
 Yes. What's wrong? 

515
00:37:55,638 --> 00:37:57,319
Luo Ren, I'm also here.

